ings, (2) MLS systems no longer displaying buyer broker compensation publicly, (3) broker compensation more openly negotiated between parties rather than commission-pool model. Florida MLS systems adaptation: Stellar MLS covering Central and South Florida largest, MIAMI Association of REALTORS MLS, BeachesMLS covering Palm Beach and Broward and Treasure Coast. Mortgage qualifying under Fannie Mae B3-3.1-01 variable income framework with 24-month averaging plus post-NAR-settlement continuity narrative addressing broker adaptation procedures plus post-settlement transaction volume plus forward-looking compensation model plus Florida market activity context. B3-3.4-02 partnership and S-corp documentation for brokerage equity K-1 distributions with 2-year personal returns plus 2-year brokerage entity returns plus shareholder or partnership agreement excerpt plus Form 1084 cash-flow analysis at brokerage entity level adding back depreciation plus business use of brokerage office plus amortization plus entity non-cash expenses with owner share at ownership percentage. Property management commission B3-3.1-01 with recurring revenue continuity narrative supported by portfolio retention metrics plus management agreements representative sample plus FREC Rule 61J2 compliance. Conventional Jumbo for HNW brokerage owners. Bank Statement Non-QM 12-24 months business bank deposits with typical 50% expense ratio for high-add-back solo brokers. P&L Statement Non-QM with CPA-prepared profit and loss for established brokerage owners. Asset-Depletion Non-QM converting liquid portfolio balance to implied monthly income for HNW post-brokerage-sale brokers. DSCR Debt Service Coverage Ratio Non-QM for investment property portfolio scaling with property rental income only qualifying plus LLC ownership accommodation. Construction-to-Permanent single-close financing for brokers building own custom home. Cash-Out Refinance for brokerage expansion plus acquisition plus partner buyout. Florida wealth migration sustaining transaction volume. Miami residential market dynamics with HNW + UHNW concentration. Post-Surfside SB 4-D condo broker work with milestone inspection and Structural Integrity Reserve Study coordination." canonical="https://stairwaymortgage.com/real-estate-professionals/real-estate-broker/">
